preference.name: CATIA_doc_attributes_form
preference.preference_description: Form type to use, attached in named reference of type catia_doc_attributes to datasets The catia_doc_attributes is created in Teamcenter during CatiaDBConfig. This setting must contain at least two fields: OEM_CATIA_Version OEM_CATIA_ENV You can choose to use another form, but it must contain two required fields listed above.
